</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">
        <a href="/">
          <img src="/gallery/logo.jpeg" alt="Logo" width="40" height="40">
          Pet Photography
        </a>
      </div>
      <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger">
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
        <span></span>
      </button>
      <ul class="nav-links" id="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/gallery">GALLERY</a></li>
        <li><a href="/how-it-works">SESSIONS</a></li>
        <li><a href="/prices">PRICES</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">ABOUT</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact">CONTACT</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="how-it-works-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <div class="hero-text">
            <h2>This is how we'll create those bright, happy pet portraits.</h2>
            <p>Don't worry if your pet is energetic, easly distractes or "doesn't listen". That's completely normal - and we work with it.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">BOOK NOW →</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-image">
            <img src="/gallery/Gallery1.jpg" alt="Pet">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Three Cards Section -->
    <section class="how-it-works-cards">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cards-grid">
          <!-- Before your session -->
          <div class="how-card card-lightblue">
            <h3>Before your session</h3>
            <p>Getting ready is simple—and no, your pet doesn't need to be perfectly trained. Curiosity, energy, and a love for treats are more than enough</p>

            <div class="card-highlight">
              <p><strong>The most important thing?</strong></p>
              <p>Bring treats. And don't overfeed your pet beforehand — a little motivation goes a long way.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card-section">
              <p><strong>YOU'RE WELCOME TO BRING</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-volleyball-icon lucide-volleyball"><path d="M11.1 7.1a16.55 16.55 0 0 1 10.9 4"/><path d="M12 12a12.6 12.6 0 0 1-8.7 5"/><path d="M16.8 13.6a16.55 16.55 0 0 1-9 7.5"/><path d="M20.7 17a12.8 12.8 0 0 0-8.7-5 13.3 13.3 0 0 1 0-10"/><path d="M6.3 3.8a16.55 16.55 0 0 0 1.9 11.5"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg> favorite toys</li>
                <li><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shirt-icon lucide-shirt"><path d="M20.38 3.46 16 2a4 4 0 0 1-8 0L3.62 3.46a2 2 0 0 0-1.34 2.23l.58 3.47a1 1 0 0 0 .99.84H6v10c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h8a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V10h2.15a1 1 0 0 0 .99-.84l.58-3.47a2 2 0 0 0-1.34-2.23z"/></svg> outfits or custumes</li>
                <li><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-venetian-mask-icon lucide-venetian-mask"><path d="M18 11c-1.5 0-2.5.5-3 2"/><path d="M4 6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v4a5 5 0 0 0 5 5 8 8 0 0 1 5 2 8 8 0 0 1 5-2 5 5 0 0 0 5-5V8a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-3a8 8 0 0 0-5 2 8 8 0 0 0-5-2z"/><path d="M6 11c1.5 0 2.5.5 3 2"/></svg> Anything that helps show your pet's personality</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- At the studio -->
          <div class="how-card card-pink">
            <h3>At the studio</h3>
            <p>Sessions take place in my home studio. Not a big commercial space—just a comfortable, pet-friendly setup where animals settle in quickly.</p>

            <div class="card-section">
              <p><strong>WHAT TO EXPECT</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li>Professional lighting, laid back atmosphere</li>
                <li>Cosy home-like environment</li>
                <li>A home-like environment</li>
                <li>You stay involved the whole time - your presence helps your pet feel safe</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- During the session -->
          <div class="how-card card-brown">
            <h3>During the session</h3>
            <p>We follow a natural flow that works for your pet. We start simple - something easy to help your pet relax and understand what's going on. Then we gradually build up to more playful, energetic moments</p>

            <div class="card-section">
              <p><strong>Think:</strong></p>
              <ul>
                <li>Jumping</li>
                <li>Sitting</li>
                <li>Catching treats</li>
              </ul>
              <p>In between we capture candid portrait moments—sitting, lying down, and those little in-between expressions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- After the session -->
    <section class="how-it-works-after">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="after-content">
          <h3>After the session</h3>
          <p>Within two weeks, you'll receive a link to your personal gallery, where you'll be able to view and choose your favorite images.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <div class="footer-col">
          <div class="footer-logo">
            <img src="/gallery/logo.jpeg" alt="Logo" width="30" height="30">
            <span>Pet Photography</span>
          </div>
          <p>Capturing the joy and personality of your beloved pets.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-col">
          <h4>QUICK LINKS</h4>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/gallery">Gallery</a></li>
            <li><a href="/how-it-works">Sessions</a></li>
            <li><a href="/prices">Prices</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-col">
          <h4>LET'S CONNECT</h4>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="https://instagram.com">Instagram</a></li>
            <li><a href="tel:+1234567890">(123) 456-7890</a></li>
            <li><a href="mailto:hello@furrytails.com">Email</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-col">
          <a href="/contact" class="footer-cta">BOOK A SESSION</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>&copy; 2026 Furry Tails Pet Photography. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    const hamburger = document.getElementById('hamburger');
    const navLinks = document.getElementById('nav-links');

    hamburger.addEventListener('click', () => {
      hamburger.classList.toggle('active');
      navLinks.style.display = navLinks.style.display === 'flex' ? 'none' : 'flex';
    });

    navLinks.querySelectorAll('a').forEach(link => {
      link.addEventListener('click', () => {
        hamburger.classList.remove('active');
        navLinks.style.display = 'none';
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
